{"tid":1364381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗遊行點解要同警察申請？","createTime":"2019-07-25T10:47:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T10:49:40.000Z","uid":12919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d26848cf5682d82d6a6ffa10bcb25b59e45975de","tid":1364381,"uid":12919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:47:02.000Z","msg":"警察都管唔到元朗<br />\n<br />\n劉業強都話會盡力勸喻村民避受衝突<br />\n<br />\n咁點解唔去鄉議局發信通知，話元朗遊行可以證明遊行本應係和平進行，過去遊行衝突都係警方引起<br />\n<br />\n今次警方發出反對通知書，可以用黎對比前幾次不反對通知書既遊行實際情況<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd5b99f7ba249238c1f81b794732435cfe903ded","tid":1364381,"uid":12919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:49:40.000Z","msg":"劉業強：鄉議局已責成元朗六鄉主席要盡力勸喻村民避免外出<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1364108\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1364108</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}